    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Maryland Public Information Act (MPIA)</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        The <strong>Maryland Public Information Act (MPIA)</strong> grants the public the right to inspect and copy public records maintained by state and local government agencies, including the City of Aberdeen.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        To request public records, complete the MPIA request form and submit it to the City Clerk's office. The City has <strong>30 days</strong> to respond to your request. Some records may require a fee to cover the cost of reproduction.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/sites/g/files/vyhlif4101/f/file/file/public_information_request_form.pdf" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gov-blue text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded hover:bg-gov-blue-dark transition-colors duration-200 text-sm">
          <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6 2a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V7.414A2 2 0 0015.414 6L12 2.586A2 2 0 0010.586 2H6zm5 6a1 1 0 10-2 0v3.586l-1.293-1.293a1 1 0 10-1.414 1.414l3 3a1 1 0 001.414 0l3-3a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L11 11.586V8z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
          Download MPIA Request Form (PDF)
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-6">How to Submit a Request</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex gap-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gov-blue text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm flex-shrink-0">1</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-navy mb-1">Complete the Form</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Download and fill out the MPIA Request Form. Be as specific as possible about the records you are requesting to help us respond quickly.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gov-blue text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm flex-shrink-0">2</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-navy mb-1">Submit to the City Clerk</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Submit your completed form by mail, in person at City Hall, or ask the City Clerk for an email submission option.</p>
            <div class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
              <a href="mailto:cityclerk@aberdeenmd.gov" class="text-xs text-gov-blue font-semibold hover:underline">Email City Clerk</a>
              <a href="{{ '/contact/' | url }}" class="text-xs text-gov-blue font-semibold hover:underline">Contact Directory</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gov-blue text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm flex-shrink-0">3</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-navy mb-1">Receive a Response</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">The City has <strong>30 days</strong> to respond. You'll be notified if records require a reproduction fee.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

